# Hospital Management System Backend

A backend application developed using Node.js, Express.js, and Mongo - DB to manage hospital operations efficiently.

## Features

* JWT Authentication
* Role-Based Authorization (Admin & Operator)
* Patient Registration
* Payment Management
* Slip Generation
* Secure REST APIs
* Mongo - DB Database Integration

## Technologies Used

* Node.js
* Express.js
* Mongo
* Mongoose
* JSON Web Token (JWT)

## User Roles

### Admin

* Manage operators
* Access all records
* Monitor hospital operations

### Operator

* Register patients
* Generate slips
* Record payments
* Manage daily operations

## Installation

1. Clone the repository
2. Install dependencies

npm install

3. Configure environment variables

Create a .env file and add:

PORT=5000
MONG0_URI=your_mongo_connection_string
JWT_SECRET=your_secret_key

4. Run the application

npm run dev

## Project Purpose

The goal of this project is to digitize hospital management processes, reduce manual work, and provide a secure system for handling patient registrations, payments, and slip generation.
 